on each genre as it comes to production, distribution and reception of popular contemporary genre film.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 0aFilm genresxHistory and criticism. 0aFilm genreszScandinavia. 0aFilm genres--Scandinavia. 0aFilm noirxHistory and criticism. 0aMotion pictureszScandinaviaxHistory. 4aFilm, Media & Cultural Studies. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / Guides & Reviews.2bisacsh1 aGustafsson, Tommy, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHakola, Outi, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHedling, Erik, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aIversen, Gunnar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKääpä, Pietari, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aKääpä, Pietari, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLaine, Kimmo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLarsson, Mariah, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLehtisalo, Anneli, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLunde, Arne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNorðfjörð, Björn Ægir, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRees, Ellen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRömpötti, Tommi, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchubart, Rikke, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSeppälä, Jaakko, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTapper, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWallengren, Ann-Kristin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb